From f7104b686cc805e6608e3bad34d55fcc404b2005 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Tzachi Shaiovitch <tzachish1@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 21 Jan 2026 10:00:15 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 02/22] feat(editor): Add Node Governance admin UI

- Add NodeGovernanceView settings page with Policies, Categories, Requests tabs
- Create Pinia store for node governance state management
- Add API client functions for all governance endpoints
- Add PoliciesTab component with CRUD operations and form modal
- Add CategoriesTab component with CRUD operations and form modal
- Add RequestsTab component with approve/reject/review workflow
- Add ReviewRequestModal for detailed request review
- Register route at /settings/node-governance with rbac protection
- Add sidebar menu item for Node Governance
- Add all i18n strings for the UI
